{"tid":1180841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［三毛末日］申請美國簽證需提交社交媒體賬號","createTime":"2019-06-01T06:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T04:27:56.000Z","uid":4942,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"982d6d73c0b3182e67eb1de292a59d44f3565361","tid":1180841,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"今天（5月31日），美國簽證發生了重大變革：非移民想要申請美國簽證，在填寫DS160申請表時都需要提供本人的社交媒體賬號，其中包括了騰訊QQ、新浪微博、豆瓣以及優酷賬號等等。 <br />\n<br />\n在2018年3月，美國國務院領事事務局發佈過一項提案：凡是要申請美國（移民或非移民）簽證的申請人，在填寫申請表時都需要提交5年內使用的社交媒體賬號。2019年5月31日，這個靴子終於落地了。"},{"pid":"e126f1e1720fde0af0c1f05f48516779942a846b","tid":1180841,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65986ef2d8bce01c8255dd3be713487406c4874b","tid":1180841,"uid":153239,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:00:50.000Z","msg":"留美是生活 反美是工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1034e3b972a9ba0e6bf1e9446772107e4e1f7f96","tid":1180841,"uid":5822,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後其他國家跟就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4ee05e455055ba2a11a5de42325de08e84ba2e","tid":1180841,"uid":27038,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"屌你，實大量帳號資料消失定啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df829ed4350a6de49b45facac62a4e0af1f91a37","tid":1180841,"uid":58008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"話無咪得？"},{"pid":"04eadb6ff7afdf39f3a431bc5af56f4ed23e3a15","tid":1180841,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1034e3b972a9ba0e6bf1e9446772107e4e1f7f96","tid":11808